<D>__{she said you were a natural. that means you can do it.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{no, it doesn't.}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{yes, it does henry.}
<P>__{(shakes him)}
<D>__{you are lophakin! a man who came from nothing. a man who's not afraid to create a new life.}
<P>__{(points)}
<D>__{a man who's in love with her!}
<A>__{henry stares at julie, mid performance, on the stage.}
<C>__{max }
<D>__{your dream is your truth is your destiny!}
